[12.72, "o", "\u001b[1mwhy (latest task log):\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.84, "o", "  # Log — Verify Stripe webhook signatures + dedupe events\r\n"]
[12.96, "o", "  - verify.go: constant-time HMAC-SHA256 over the raw body with the signing secret; a\r\n"]
[13.08, "o", "    missing / stale / mismatched Stripe-Signature is rejected 400 before any handler runs.\r\n"]
[13.2, "o", "  - Dedupe by Stripe event id (seen-events table + unique index) — a redelivery is a no-op.\r\n"]
[13.7, "o", "  - Gate green: gofmt clean, go build/vet/test ./... pass; added a replay + bad-signature test.\r\n"]
